Package com.fssa.freshnest.model

Class Still

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.freshnest.model.Still
public class Still extends Object
The `Still` class represents a photographic still captured by a user within the FreshNest application. It encapsulates information such as the image URL, user details, name, date, time, and various flags indicating whether the still is a favorite, marked for deletion, or subject to updates.
Author:
SusikumarPitchaimuth
